      "credentials": { "gmailOAuth2": { "id": "kNJFk3eoaf9XE63X", "name": "Ryan's Gmail" } }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2. ERROR HANDLING WORKFLOW\n\nSet this as the **Error Workflow** for the other two workflows (Settings -> Error Workflow). Then ANY unhandled failure anywhere triggers this:\n\n1. **Detect** - Error Trigger fires on any failed execution.\n2. **Extract** - pulls workflow, failed node, message, execution URL.\n3. **Classify** - auth/quota/rate-limit => HIGH, else STANDARD.\n4. **Log** - appends to the ErrorLog tab (audit trail).\n5. **Alert / Escalate** - HIGH -> urgent escalation email; otherwise standard notification.\n\nDemonstrates: error detection, logging, alerting, severity-based escalation. Pairs with the retry + model-fallback + continue-on-error built into Workflow 1.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 440,
        "color": 2
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, 0],
      "id": "9dfb8a7d-c099-44d5-a44c-3ecb4fe8b7ac",
      "name": "Error WF Note"
    }
  ],
  "pinData": {},
